*xmobar-0.23.1 (01 Jun 2015)

  01 Jun 2015; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +xmobar-0.23.1.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*xmobar-0.23 (09 Apr 2015)

  09 Apr 2015; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +xmobar-0.23.ebuild:
  Bump xmobar to 0.23, thanks to wolfwood for reporting.

*xmobar-0.22.1 (25 Oct 2014)

